<div style="font-family:system-ui,-apple-system,Segoe UI,Roboto,Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;line-height:1.55;color:#111">
  <h2 style="margin:0 0 12px">🙏 Cow Puja – Payment received</h2>
  <p>Dear {{customerName}},</p>
  <p>We have received your payment for the Cow Puja. Our team will review your request and confirm the puja date shortly.</p>

  <table cellspacing="0" cellpadding="8" style="border-collapse:collapse;margin-top:12px">
    <tr>
      <td style="border:1px solid #e5e7eb"><strong>Order ID</strong></td>
      <td style="border:1px solid #e5e7eb"><code>{{orderId}}</code></td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td style="border:1px solid #e5e7eb"><strong>Amount</strong></td>
      <td style="border:1px solid #e5e7eb">{{amountINR}} ({{currency}})</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td style="border:1px solid #e5e7eb"><strong>Preferred Date</strong></td>
      <td style="border:1px solid #e5e7eb">{{#if preferredDate}}{{preferredDate}}{{else}}Not specified (we will book earliest available){{/if}}</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td style="border:1px solid #e5e7eb"><strong>Gotra</strong></td>
      <td style="border:1px solid #e5e7eb">{{gotra}}</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td style="border:1px solid #e5e7eb"><strong>Purpose / Sankalpam</strong></td>
      <td style="border:1px solid #e5e7eb">{{sankalpam}}</td>
    </tr>
  </table>

  <p style="margin-top:16px">You will receive another email once the puja date is confirmed.</p>
  <p>With blessings,<br/>Shri Devraha Baba Ashram</p>
</div>
